Package: libjson-api-perl
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, perl, libjson-perl, liburi-encode-perl, libwww-perl
Description: Module to interact with a JSON API
 This module wraps JSON and LWP::UserAgent to create a flexible
 utility for accessing APIs that accept/provide JSON data.
 .
 It supports all the options LWP supports, including authentication.
